36:08.209 --> 36:11.256
- I want you to get better.

36:11.299 --> 36:13.388
- I'm sorry.

36:13.432 --> 36:15.521
I need help.

36:15.564 --> 36:21.353
♪

36:21.396 --> 36:23.311
- We all need help.

36:23.355 --> 36:25.444
