36:55.125 --> 36:57.127
- It's no big deal.

36:58.955 --> 37:00.522
- Thank you.

37:00.566 --> 37:03.177
Seriously.

37:03.221 --> 37:05.440
How amazing are you?

37:07.703 --> 37:10.576
